data.description: Welcome to this Charming 3 Bedroom! Large Family room perfect for entertaining. High Beam Ceilings, Brick Wood Burning Fireplace and Large window adds Character to this home. The Galley Kitchen and separate Dining area are a nice touch. Primary Bedroom is a nice size w/walk in closet an updated Shower. Back yard is spacious and the 2 storage sheds will remain with the home. A/C is about 8 years old, Water Heater 5 years and Roof 10-years old. 2023-11-19
